    <p><strong>Key specs:</strong> Steel burr · internal stepped adjustment · 25g capacity · Espresso suitability: Pressurized-only.</p>
    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It offers the most reliable cup quality per dollar in the entry budget tier.</p>
    <p><strong>Retention/static note:</strong> Very low retention, with minor fines clinging around the catch cup after dry-weather grinding.</p>

    <h3>$50-$80 tier winner: 1Zpresso Q Air</h3>
